{
  "texts": [
    "The CAMEL dataset features an extensive collection of around 584K instructions, among which 107K have been translated into multiple languages.",
    "This dataset provides a wide array of dialogue resources covering both multilingual and code domains.",
    "The datasets introduces a communication agent framework called \"role-playing\" generated through three types of prompts and involving two contexts: \"AI Society\" and \"Programming.\"",
    "• Chatgpt corpus foot_63.",
    "The Chatgpt corpus dataset contains 3.27M instances of the model engaging in self-conversation."
  ]
}